0.1 (2010-04-04)
* first release
* 4 different widgets: statistics, top reads, top comments, top trackbacks
* statistics: get counters for posts, comments and trackbacks (get total for each one)
* statistics: if postcount module is installed, get post read counters (min, max, sum, avg)
* top reads, top comments, top trackbacks: get top 'x' posts reads/comments/trackbacks
